summary: I'm so fucking sick of dumbasses calling out PewDiePie or implying he's spreading racism and antisemitism for youth. And the...
body:
I’m so fucking sick of dumbasses calling out PewDiePie or implying he’s spreading racism and antisemitism for youth. And the worst fucking part is whenever I call someone out on their bullshit because all they do is read sleazy clickbait articles then make shit up about the real world, they just block me after trying to give a rebuttal.

That’s not how arguing works. Thats not how anyone learns anything you ignorant twats. At this point I’m not even angry we disagree. I’m just fucking livid you’re going to ignore an issue you make such a fuss about as soon as someone disagrees with you. You’re a damn coward just like my fucking Cheeto of a president.

Get some confidence and try to convince me. I don’t viciously attack the posts I comment on, I just try and make points against what you’re saying because I think I have solid evidence that suggests otherwise and you’re being misled. So if somehow you read this @rootbeergoddess @sellerofqualitykazoos (cant tag because you blocked me and ran away without proving anything) then prove me wrong.

I’m so tired of you lazy negative pricks causing drama just to get attention and follow a moral bandwagon. Do some research for crying out loud.
